==Bosnian==
===Etymology===
Old Church Slavonic '''[[бъіти]]''' (''byti''), from Proto-Indo-European ''*bheu(H)-'' (whence also English [[be]]).

===Verb===
'''biti''' 
# to [[be]], exist

